本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:王麗婷研究生(外文):Wang Li-Ting　　論文名稱:共同基金流量與投資績效之實證研究論文名稱(外文):The Empirical Study of Mutual Fund Flow and Performance指導教授:程言信指導教授(外文):Yen-Shin Cheng口試委員:程言信、曾麗弘、馬泰成口試委員(外文):Yen-Shin Cheng、Li-Hong Zeng、Tai-Cheng Ma口試日期:2014-05-15學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立高雄應用科技大學系所名稱:金融資訊研究所學門:商業及管理學門學類:財務金融學類論文出版年:2014畢業學年度:102語文別:中文論文頁數:70中文關鍵詞:基金流量、投資組合、投資績效外文關鍵詞:Mutual Fund Flows、Investment Portfolio、Investment Performance相關次數:

被引用:1點閱:161評分:下載:0書目收藏:0



    本文採用股票型國內投資基金資料為標的，期間取自2003年1月至2013年6月的月資料，共取得123檔基金之126個月觀察值。先利用非恆定計量模型檢視整體股票型國內投資基金的申購量、贖回量、淨值與基金規模之間的關係，其次利用共同基金申購量與贖回量來擬定各種投資進場策略，並且分析藉由不同的投資組合策略來探討前期共同基金流量對基金續效的影響，嘗試藉此來尋找較佳的投資策略。     實證結果如下：1.  基金淨值顯著影響基金之申購量及贖回量，且因果關係呈現單向影響。而基金規模與淨值及申購量與贖回量各自存在著因果關係。2.  在衝擊反應分析下，所有變數對自身的衝擊於期初皆有正向反應；申購量及贖回量對淨值之衝擊於期初2個月為正向反應。3.  採用基金流量所構成的投資組合策略中，以標準化流出量最高者相較於其他流量策略之報酬較佳，再與大盤的績效相較之下，亦會有顯著的優於大盤。4.  採用標準化流量構建之投資組合策略，於不同的進場投資策略中，其風險均無顯著差異。5.  透過基金流量的計量統計分析實證，依據基金流量所建構的投資組合策略結果獲得支持。

In this paper, we use the data of domestic equity funds from Jan. 2003 to June 2013, that is, a total of 126 month observation data for each of 123 funds. In the empirical study, we first adopt non-stationary-metric model to inspect the relationship among the quantity of purchase, quantity of redemption, net value and the scale of the fund of the entire domestic equity funds; meanwhile, the quantity of purchase and quantity of redemption of the mutual fund were used to prepare all kinds of investment timing strategies, furthermore, through the analysis of different investment portfolio strategies, the influence of the fund flow of the previous fund on the fund performance was then investigated, by doing so, it is hoped that better investment strategy can be found out.     The empirical results are as in the followings:1.  The net value of fund significantly affects the quantity of purchase and quantity of redemption of the fund, and the cause-and-effect relationship shows the influence to be one way. Moreover, respective cause-and-effect relationship exists between the scale of the fund and the net value of the fund as well as between the quantity of purchase of the fund and the quantity of redemption of the fund.2.  Under the impulse response analysis, all the variables show positive response on its own impulse in the initial stage; meanwhile, the impulses of quantity of purchase and quantity of redemption on the net value show positive responses in the first two months.3.  In the investment portfolio strategies made up of fund flow, the one with the highest standardized flow shows better earning as compared to that of other flow strategies. Moreover, when it is compared to the performance of stock weighted average index, it is obviously superior to it.4.  For investment portfolio strategies made up of standardized flow, it was found that its risk does not show significant difference under investment strategies of different entrance timings.5.  Through the empirical study of quantitative statistical analysis of fund flow, it was found that the result of investment portfolio strategy constructed based on fund flow has gained its ground of support.

